HEADWORD: coenobitical
<hw>coenobitical</hw></mhw> <pos>adj.</pos>
<def>of or relating to or befitting cenobites or their practices of
communal living. Opposite of <ant>eremitic</ant>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> cenobitic, cenobitical.</syn>⟦br⟧
